  "detailed_description": "<strong>Webbed </strong> is the story of a happy little spider on an adventure to save her boyfriend from a big mean bowerbird.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/857f90c44e09ad98512c72a3dcf8af14.poster.avif?t=1748008096\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/857f90c44e09ad98512c72a3dcf8af14.webm?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/857f90c44e09ad98512c72a3dcf8af14.mp4?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the dangerous wilderness with nothing but your webs and your wits. Practise the art of web swinging to speed your way through the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/b8bee4e2d3a2e33a6f255e820613b546.poster.avif?t=1748008096\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/b8bee4e2d3a2e33a6f255e820613b546.webm?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/b8bee4e2d3a2e33a6f255e820613b546.mp4?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Leave your own unique mark by spinning webs through the interconnected world. Stick webs to almost anything and use them to create your own paths.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/3a0ce7442b7918896faaebfd6dd65fa9.poster.avif?t=1748008096\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/3a0ce7442b7918896faaebfd6dd65fa9.webm?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/3a0ce7442b7918896faaebfd6dd65fa9.mp4?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Make friends with bugs, and dance with them. Some bugs could use a little help from a friend and might even join your rescue effort in return!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Webbed </strong> is the story of a happy little spider on an adventure to save her boyfriend from a big mean bowerbird.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/857f90c44e09ad98512c72a3dcf8af14.poster.avif?t=1748008096\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/857f90c44e09ad98512c72a3dcf8af14.webm?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/857f90c44e09ad98512c72a3dcf8af14.mp4?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the dangerous wilderness with nothing but your webs and your wits. Practise the art of web swinging to speed your way through the world!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/b8bee4e2d3a2e33a6f255e820613b546.poster.avif?t=1748008096\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/b8bee4e2d3a2e33a6f255e820613b546.webm?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/b8bee4e2d3a2e33a6f255e820613b546.mp4?t=1748008096\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Leave your own unique mark by spinning webs through the interconnected world. Stick webs to almost anything and use them to create your own paths.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1390350/extras/3a0ce7442b7918896faaebfd6dd65fa9.poster.avif?t=1748008096\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.